{"tid":2176723,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：抗疫落幕，演員離開舞台。何柏良宣布退出商台的每日訪問節目。我日前在家中設壇，做了法會，香港轉運，結束鬧劇。","createTime":"2020-08-27T09:10:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-27T09:40:53.000Z","uid":271829,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"110ba1eb4cbdc523768479b2455da8e3fab5bf7a","tid":2176723,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wqcVoZd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwqcVoZd.png&h=9c159389&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲：抗疫落幕，演員離開舞台。何柏良宣布退出商業電台的每日訪問節目，他寄望大家用科學來看疫病。他也許在暗示，香港之前的防疫是政治，不是科學。<br />\n我日前在家中設壇，做了時輪金剛法會。香港轉運。<br />\n遲些機緣到了，補做去年大黑天金剛除障法會，結束鬧劇。要先用時輪金剛法會扭轉時空，才可以補做去年停做的大黑天金剛除障法會。<br />\n（圖片來源：網絡）"},{"pid":"4043d01d0ba86d2899f823d3777338d5a5ad9330","tid":2176723,"uid":57844,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"陳雲未食藥"},{"pid":"933b55075414af4f16c99084d470f0f196ac87f9","tid":2176723,"uid":287051,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:14:14.000Z","msg":"陳雲要轉醫生"},{"pid":"0b07290ce10689705699a71a579b9c1a088d5047","tid":2176723,"uid":14605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:14:16.000Z","msg":"顛撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25d4cb05ce664b11b83dd06b69ff7911a67b1b46","tid":2176723,"uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:14:42.000Z","msg":"青山走犯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f799d29e972c2b14c7f5cca843b5d204c696ae3e","tid":2176723,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"國師救港"},{"pid":"6dc6f5f94c4a6fc03857a959b94a520d49ac7a53","tid":2176723,"uid":13663,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTim